                          July 1 (Bloomberg) -- Bloomberg's Elliott Gotkine reports on the dispute over the assets of L’Oreal SA heiress Liliane Bettencourt in France, as a trial opens over whether the 87-year-old was manipulated into giving a friend about a billion euros ($1.23 billion) in gifts. (Source: Bloomberg)  
                           

     
